social_posts.post_text:
An absolutely perfect date night @edgesteakhouse located inside @fsdenver 💘

From carefully crafted cocktails, a full raw bar, excellent meat and fish selections and  positively delectable sides this meal was top notch. 

I loved the creativity of my Thai inspired Sea Bass and of course can you really go wrong with creamy Mac and cheese topped with succulent lobster? If I didn't recommend that Mac it would basically be a crime! 

The torched Salmon Nigiri was the perfect bite to kick off the meal and had me wanting to come back asap to sample more from their raw bar! 

And of course you must end with dessert, and though I strayed away from my usual Crème Brûlée, the Sticky Toffee Pudding essentially left me no choice, and I can assure you there were zero regrets. 

If you're looking for a place to enjoy after work cocktails (order the Smoked Old Fashioned and thank me later), brunch, date night, or heck just to have a parents night out @edgesteakhouse @fsdenver will absolutely deliver! 

Thank you so much for having us. We can't wait to come back! #hosted
